  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of RGH-188 (Cariprazine) in Bipolar Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study of RGH-188 (Cariprazine) in Bipolar Depression</official_title>
